SELECT 'CreateDeliveryLine' || '::' || "DeliveryLine"."ID"  AS "ID",
       "DeliveryLine"."ID"                                  AS "DeliveryLine",
       "DeliveryLine"."CreationTime"                        AS "Time",
       "DeliveryLine"."CreatedBy_ID"                        AS "ExecutedBy",
       "DeliveryLine"."CreationExecutionType"               AS "ExecutionType",
       "DeliveryLine"."Delivery_ID"                         AS "Delivery"
FROM (
    SELECT
        "DeliveryLine"."ID"                    AS "ID",
        "DeliveryLine"."CreationTime"          AS "CreationTime",
        "DeliveryLine"."CreatedBy_ID"          AS "CreatedBy_ID",
        "DeliveryLine"."CreationExecutionType" AS "CreationExecutionType",
        "Delivery"."ID"                        AS "Delivery_ID"
    FROM (
        SELECT
            "DeliveryLine"."ID"                    AS "ID",
            "DeliveryLine"."CreationTime"          AS "CreationTime",
            "DeliveryLine"."CreatedBy_ID"          AS "CreatedBy_ID",
            "DeliveryLine"."CreationExecutionType" AS "CreationExecutionType",
            "DeliveryLine"."Delivery_ID"           AS "Header_ID"
        FROM "o_custom_DeliveryLine" AS "DeliveryLine"
        ORDER BY "DeliveryLine"."Delivery_ID"
    ) AS "DeliveryLine"
    LEFT JOIN "o_custom_Delivery" AS "Delivery"
        ON "DeliveryLine"."Header_ID" = "Delivery"."ID"
    ORDER BY "DeliveryLine"."ID"
) AS "DeliveryLine"
WHERE "DeliveryLine"."CreationTime" IS NOT NULL
